{"tid":1697048,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"TikTok致信美國國會 稱用戶數據儲存在美國","createTime":"2019-11-06T14:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T15:20:23.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4249b2a5bfb9e8bef9fa48a752a8b2b1fed54b57","tid":1697048,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"TikTok致信美國國會 稱用戶數據儲存在美國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2491801/TikTok%E8%87%B4%E4%BF%A1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%20%E7%A8%B1%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E5%84%B2%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2491801%2FTikTok%25E8%2587%25B4%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2583%2520%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%2584%25B2%25E5%25AD%2598%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNW%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=b40ee7e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2491801/TikTok%E8%87%B4%E4%BF%A1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%20%E7%A8%B1%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E5%84%B2%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B</a><br />\n<br />\n抖音海外版TikTok在美國當地時間周二致信美國國會，自稱為一家獨立運營公司，TikTok美國用戶數據全部儲存在美國境內，不會在中國儲美國用戶數據。信中提及，已聘請一家美國審計公司分析公司對數據安全做法，計劃成立一個由外部專家組成的委員會，咨詢有關內容管理和透明度。<br />\n<br />\nTikTok強調，該平台不會接受任何政治廣告。另外，在信中，TikTok指出，公司主要投資者是大型投資機構，包括軟銀、紅杉資本、KKR、General Atlantic和Hillhouse Capital Group等。<br />\n<br />\n該信由TikTok美國總經理Vanessa Pappas簽發，落款為當地時間周一。<br />\n<br />\n其後，美國國會參議院司法委員會，舉行一個關於美國公民個人資料安全問題的聽證會。主持聽證會的共和黨參議員Josh Hawley對TikTok儲存美國用戶數據提出質疑。惟TikTok高層未出席聽證會。"},{"pid":"97ab301a230ff161fe42a40be336dd933259ea18","tid":1697048,"uid":12864,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:06:29.000Z","msg":"儲存啫，唔代表唔會運返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ede5240962e7f9befe8573edbea10fcf95df2a1","tid":1697048,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c154559136fa7f88a8eed482efb4f880e178218e","tid":1697048,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鎖國啦! 吊你老母, 咁撚強大, 使咩吼住外國市場 ?"}]}